import React, { Component } from "react"; import axios from 'axios'; export default class Pricing extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = this.state = { countryName: '', countryCode: '', }; } getGeoInfo = () => { axios.get('https://ipapi.co/json/').then((response) => { let data = response.data; this.setState({ countryName: data.country_name, countryCode: data.country_calling_code }); }).catch((error) => { console.log(error); }); }; componentWillMount() { } componentWillUnmount() { } componentDidMount() { this.getGeoInfo(); } //
